content:
Also add 5% of the proceeds goes to two non-profits. STOCKTON SHELTER FOR THE HOMELESS
Stockton Shelter for the Homeless (SSH), offers health care for the homeless veterans (HCHV). We assist homeless veterans with health care, financial assistance, and housing and GULISI COMMUNITY PRIMARY SCHOOL
Gulisi Community Primary School is an elementary school. It was founded 15 years ago. They help students with scholarships to continue on with their education. Located in Dangriga, Belize.
